g.text: Title: ATX Power Supply Distribution Board
Connect a LED as an standby indicator.
Do not use this connection for high power
The switch will short the PS_ON connector
with the Ground and start the power supply.
When using a switch with LED lighting then
use a one of the power rails to power the
led seperately and put a pull-up resistor
